6. If a third‑party app, contact that app’s support—some apps list but don’t actually support GPT‑5 yet.\\n\\nIf you want, tell me:\\n- where you set it (web UI, mobile, API, third‑party app)\\n- what you see (model name displayed, or example response headers)\\n\\nI can give next steps specific to your situation or help draft a support message.\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"stop\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":613,\"promptTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":631}}}"}}
